# News Flow App

A modern, responsive news application that provides real-time news updates across various categories including Cricket, India, Technology, Politics, Business, and Entertainment.

## Features

- 📰 Real-time news updates
- 🔍 Search functionality for specific news topics
- 📚 Bookmark favorite articles
- 🌙 Dark/Light theme toggle
- 📅 Time-based filtering (Today/This Week)
- 🔐 User authentication
- 📱 Responsive design for all devices

